## Workflow (reference)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
  start[Design input URL or screenshot]
  decompose[Decompose layout and UI blocks]
  mapComp[Map blocks to ui/antd and shell patterns]
  mapType[Map text to figmaTypography or token typography]
  mapColor[Map colors to semantic tokens]
  gapComp{Gap component not in barrel or unclear}
  gapTok{Gap no semantic token}
  askUser[Stop and ask user]
  implement[Implement with tokens only]
  verify[Checklist and build if needed]
  start --> decompose --> mapComp --> mapType --> mapColor
  mapColor --> gapComp
  gapComp -->|yes| askUser
  gapComp -->|no| gapTok
  gapTok -->|yes| askUser
  gapTok -->|no| implement --> verify
```
